about.summary: A port of node.js's EventEmitter to python.

name: pyee
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyee" %}
{% set version = "5.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4ec22817297b7024f89721cc34f790ee2767c5b5ca44284c565ee643abafbe32
  patches:
    - setup.patch

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - pip
    - vcversioner
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pyee

about:
  home: https://github.com/jfhbrook/pyee
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENSE'
  summary: "A port of node.js's EventEmitter to python."
  doc_url: https://pyee.readthedocs.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/jfhbrook/pyee

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kiwi0fruit
